repos.name: assemble-middleware-anchors

repos.name: assemble-middleware-contextual
repos.description: Assemble middleware for generating a JSON file containing the context of each page. Basic middleware to help see what's happening in the build.

repos.name: assemble-middleware-decompress
repos.description: Assemble plugin for extracting zip, tar and tar.gz archives.

repos.name: assemble-middleware-download
repos.description: Assemble middleware for downloading files from GitHub.

repos.description: Assemble middleware (v0.5.0) for preventing drafts from being rendered.

repos.description: Assemble middleware for adding i18n support to projects.

repos.description: Assemble middleware for creating RSS feeds with Assemble. (NOT published yet!)

repos.description: Assemble middleware for displaying a word-count, and estimated reading time on blog posts or pages.
